OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be dry with some
OL,6,Fsunshine in the morning. Clouding over
OL,7,Ffrom the southwest in the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some showery rain extending
OL,9,Fnortheast later. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSome showery and mainly light
OL,12,Frain will clear northeast through the
OL,13,Fevening. Then it will stay dry
OL,14,Fovernight with perhaps the odd clear
OL,15,Fspell developing by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
