OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FSome bright spells possible
OL,6,Fat first, but soon clouding over with
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, these
OL,8,Fturning heavy in places in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. A little less warm than
OL,10,FFriday.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fon Sunday with a chance of showers.
OL,14,FRain for a time on Monday, otherwise
OL,15,Fsunny spells and a few showers
OL,16,Fcontinuing through Tuesday. Remaining
OL,17,Fcooler with some overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
